CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 20, 1962, pg. 10 reads:" 'Y' Ranch hands In Big '62 Round-Up - Sales Talk - Team captains of W.H. Coleman's division for the 1962 membership enrollment are listening to J.D. Davis Sr., member of the branch board, give a sales talk. Left to right: Benjamin McLin, W.H. Coleman, Mr. Lewis [Davis], William Albea, Dr. W.V. Waller and Paul E. Thompson."
TitMainTitle: J.D. Davis Sr. speaking a podium, with, from left: Benjamin McLin, W.H. Coleman, William Albea, Dr. W.V. Waller, and Paul E. Thompson, standing behind folding table with documents and film projector, in Centre Avenue YMCA during 1962 membership campaign
